<h3 class="bonfire">Elden Ring&nbsp;Bull-Goat's Talisman Notes &amp; Tips</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>Sell Value:&nbsp;<img title="runes-currency-elden-ring-wiki-guide-18" src="/file/Elden-Ring/runes-currency-elden-ring-wiki-guide-18.png" alt="runes currency elden ring wiki guide 18" width="18" height="18">&nbsp;1000</li> 
 <li>Displays a <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Poise" href="/Poise" target="">Poise</a> stat increase of 33%.</li> 
 <li>Thematically matches the <a class="wiki_link wiki_tooltip" title="Elden Ring Bull-Goat Set" href="/Bull-Goat+Set">Bull-Goat Set</a>.&nbsp;</li> 
</ul> 
